.TH LVMDBUSD 8 "LVM TOOLS #VERSION#" "Red Hat Inc" \" -*- nroff -*-
.
.SH NAME
.
lvmdbusd \(em LVM D-Bus daemon
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.
.na
.B lvmdbusd
.RB [ --debug ]
.RB [ --udev ]
.ad
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.
lvmdbusd is a service which provides a D-Bus API
to the logical volume manager (LVM).
Run
.BR lvmdbusd (8)
as root.
.
.SH OPTIONS
.
.TP 8
.B --debug
Enable debug statements
.
.TP
.B --udev
Use udev events to trigger updates
.
